longBusinessSummary: Enterprise Financial Services Group, Inc., through its wholly-owned subsidiary, Enterprise Bank, provides various banking products and services to small business entrepreneurs in Western Pennsylvania. The company offers checking and savings accounts. It also provides commercial mortgage and term loans, commercial lines of credit, small business administration and government loans, construction and development finance, equipment finance, and working capital finance. In addition, the company offers credit and debit cards; insurance products; remote deposit services; and merchant services. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Allison Park, Pennsylvania.
